"{\"uid\": \"egyptindependent.com-biography-of-a-champion-egyptian-weightlifter-sarah-samir-wins-silver-at-the-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Egyptian weightlifter Sarah Samirwon the silver medal in weightlifting at the Paris 2024 Olympic Games, being held in France, on Sunday evening.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 8, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egyptians\", \"score\": 0.8921523526540699, \"rank\": 0.11152236079430859, \"text\": \"Egyptian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egyptians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egyptians\"}, {\"begin\": 118, \"end\": 124, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9997740532308677, \"rank\": 0.00014521464562083908, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 33rd edition of the Paris 2024 Olympic Games kicked off on July 26 and ends on Sunday.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 236, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Samircame in second place after lifting 151kg in the clean and jerk and 117kg in the snatch competitions for the 81 kg weight class - a total of 268 kg in the weightlifting competitions.\", \"from\": 238, \"to\": 424, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She previously won the bronze medal at the 2016 Rio de Janeiro Olympics.\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 498, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Samir was born on January 1, 1998 in the city of Ismailia, to a rural family in the village of al-Hawania.\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 608, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 502, \"end\": 507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samir_Nabi\", \"score\": 0.533289636383995, \"rank\": 0.47129671255464445, \"text\": \"Samir\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samir_Nabi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samir_Nabi\"}, {\"begin\": 551, \"end\": 559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ismailia\", \"score\": 0.9999932491808108, \"rank\": 6.712591298986035e-06, \"text\": \"Ismailia\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ismailia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ismailia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ever since early childhood she dreamt of becoming a world champion in weightlifting, and received encouragement from her family to continue the path of success.\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 770, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The passion ran in her family, as Samir loved weightlifting because of her father who practiced the same sport, while her brother Mohamed was a weightlifting coach.\", \"from\": 772, \"to\": 936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 806, \"end\": 811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samir_Nabi\", \"score\": 0.533289636383995, \"rank\": 0.47129671255464445, \"text\": \"Samir\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samir_Nabi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samir_Nabi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She would go with her older brother to his training sessions, where she discovered her unique talent in weightlifting.\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 1056, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Samir then joined the Military Institution School team after encouragement from her brother.\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1058, \"end\": 1063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samir_Nabi\", \"score\": 0.533289636383995, \"rank\": 0.47129671255464445, \"text\": \"Samir\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samir_Nabi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samir_Nabi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the age of eleven, she participated in her first championship and achieved first place, quickly joining the Egyptian weightlifting team despite her young age.\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1263, \"end\": 1271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egyptians\", \"score\": 0.8921523526540699, \"rank\": 0.11152236079430859, \"text\": \"Egyptian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egyptians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egyptians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2014 at the Nanjing Youth Olympics in China, Samir won the gold medal in the women's 63 kg weight and made history as the the first Egyptian weightlifter to win an Olympic medal in the women's competition.\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1523, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1356, \"end\": 1361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9441309579223146, \"rank\": 0.05812284086523494, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1363, \"end\": 1368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samir_Nabi\", \"score\": 0.533289636383995, \"rank\": 0.47129671255464445, \"text\": \"Samir\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samir_Nabi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samir_Nabi\"}, {\"begin\": 1450, \"end\": 1458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egyptians\", \"score\": 0.8921523526540699, \"rank\": 0.11152236079430859, \"text\": \"Egyptian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egyptians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egyptians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the age of 18, Samir sacrificed her high school exams in order to join the Egyptian weightlifting team camp in Uzbekistan, in preparation for participating in the 2016 Rio de Janeiro Olympics in Brazil.\", \"from\": 1525, \"to\": 1730, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1543, \"end\": 1548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samir_Nabi\", \"score\": 0.533289636383995, \"rank\": 0.47129671255464445, \"text\": \"Samir\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samir_Nabi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samir_Nabi\"}, {\"begin\": 1603, \"end\": 1611, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egyptians\", \"score\": 0.8921523526540699, \"rank\": 0.11152236079430859, \"text\": \"Egyptian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egyptians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Egyptians\"}, {\"begin\": 1639, \"end\": 1649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\", \"score\": 0.6304634000577598, \"rank\": 0.46081421741745665, \"text\": \"Uzbekistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uzbekistan\"}, {\"begin\": 1723, \"end\": 1729, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9321983308213617, \"rank\": 0.07194933787634016, \"text\": \"Brazil\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She managed to win the bronze medal at the 2016 Rio Olympics in weightlifting for the 68 kg weight class.\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1837, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"With this win, Samir became the youngest Egyptian to ever win an Olympic medal at the age of 18.\", \"from\": 1839, \"to\": 1935, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1854, \"end\": 1859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samir_Nabi\", \"score\": 0.533289636383995, \"rank\": 0.47129671255464445, \"text\": \"Samir\"